{"comments":"Service Worker registration and communication\n\nPWA support with service worker lifecycle management.\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Offline.ServiceWorker as SW\n\n-- Register service worker\nregistration <- SW.register \"/sw.js\"\n\n-- Check for updates\nSW.checkForUpdate registration\n\n-- Listen for state changes\nSW.onStateChange registration \\state ->\n  case state of\n    SW.Installing -> showToast \"Installing update...\"\n    SW.Activated -> showToast \"App updated!\"\n    _ -> pure unit\n\n-- Post message to SW\nSW.postMessage registration { type: \"SKIP_WAITING\" }\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Service Worker Registration\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[67,41],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Offline/ServiceWorker.purs","start":[67,1]},"title":"Registration"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[71,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Offline/ServiceWorker.purs","start":[71,3]},"title":"Installing"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Offline/ServiceWorker.purs","start":[72,3]},"title":"Installed"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[73,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Offline/ServiceWorker.purs","start":[73,3]},"title":"Activating"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[74,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Offline/ServiceWorker.purs","start":[74,3]},"title":"Activated"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[75,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Offline/ServiceWorker.purs","start":[75,3]},"title":"Redundant"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{